LogicalColumn.name: Days Open
LogicalColumn.Description: "Age of open activities in days, from Activity Actual Start Date to last data warehouse refresh date"

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_DAY , "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ACTIVITY_F_Actual_End_Date"."ACTUAL_START_DT", IFNULL("Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."Fact_W_ACTIVITY_F_Actual_End_Date"."ACTUAL_END_DT", VALUEOF("Warehouse Refresh Date"."LAST_REFRESH_DT")))

LogicalColumn.name: Days Open Category
LogicalColumn.Description: "Activity Days Open Category by number of days open. Categories are A: <= 5, B: 6 - 10, C: 11 - 15, D: 16 - 30, E: 31 - 45, F: 46 - 60 and G: 61+"

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" IS NULL THEN 'A: <= 5' WHEN "%2" <= 5 THEN 'A: <= 5' WHEN "%2" <= 10 THEN 'B: 6 - 10' WHEN "%2" <= 15 THEN 'C: 11 - 15' WHEN "%2" <= 30 THEN 'D: 16 - 30' WHEN "%2" <= 45 THEN 'E: 31 - 45' WHEN "%2" <= 60 THEN 'F: 46 - 60' ELSE 'G: 61+' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Dim - Activity"."Actual Start Date" IS NULL THEN 'A: <= 5' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Activity"."Days Open" <= 5 THEN 'A: <= 5' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Activity"."Days Open" <= 10 THEN 'B: 6 - 10' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Activity"."Days Open" <= 15 THEN 'C: 11 - 15' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Activity"."Days Open" <= 30 THEN 'D: 16 - 30' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Activity"."Days Open" <= 45 THEN 'E: 31 - 45' WHEN "Core"."Dim - Activity"."Days Open" <= 60 THEN 'F: 46 - 60' ELSE 'G: 61+' END
